#analysis about characters per positive/negative/neutral tweet

plt.rcParams['font.size'] = '25'
df = dfFilter.copy()
yCol = 'Label'
xCol = "NumCharacters"
for yValue in df[yCol].unique():
#     yValue = "Positive"
    plt.figure(figsize=(20,10))
    xValue = df[(df[yCol] == yValue)][xCol].values
    ax = sns.histplot(xValue, kde = True)
    ax.set_xlabel('Character Count', fontsize=20)
    ax.set_ylabel('Frequency', fontsize=20)
    ax.title.set_text("Histogram - Characters Per %s Tweet"%yValue)

plt.rcParams['font.size'] = '25'
df = dfFilter.copy()
yCol = 'Label'
xCol = "NumCharacters"
for yValue in df[yCol].unique():
#     yValue = "Positive"
    plt.figure(figsize=(20,10))
    xValue = df[(df[yCol] == yValue)][xCol].values
    kwargs = {'cumulative': True}
    ax = sns.distplot(xValue, hist_kws=kwargs, kde_kws=kwargs)
    ax.set_xlabel('Character Count', fontsize=20)
    ax.set_ylabel('Cumulative Probability', fontsize=20)
    ax.title.set_text("Empirical CDF - Characters Per %s Tweet"%yValue)

In [103]:
#top 10 unigram for positive, negative and neutral tweet

yCol = 'Label'
xCol = 'cleanTweet'
ncols = len(dfFilter[yCol].unique())
fig, ax = plt.subplots(nrows = 1, ncols = ncols, figsize=(20,10))
for no, yValue in enumerate(df[yCol].unique()):
    cleanTweetArray = dfFilter[dfFilter[yCol] == yValue][xCol].map(lambda x:re.split(' ', x)).array
    #flatten list of array
    allTokens = [i for i in list(itertools.chain(*cleanTweetArray)) if i!='']

    num = 10
    dfCount = pd.Series(allTokens).value_counts()[:num].reset_index()
    dfCount.columns = ["Unigram", "Frequency"]
    dfCount.sort_values("Frequency", inplace = True)
    dfCount.plot.barh(x='Unigram', y = 'Frequency', title = "Top 10 Unigram - %s"%yValue, ax=ax[no], legend=False)
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
In [104]:
#top 10 bigram for positive, negative and neutral tweet


yCol = 'Label'
xCol = 'cleanTweet'
ncols = len(dfFilter[yCol].unique())
fig, ax = plt.subplots(nrows = 1, ncols = ncols, figsize=(20,10))
for no, yValue in enumerate(df[yCol].unique()):
    cleanTweetArray = dfFilter[dfFilter[yCol] == yValue][xCol].map(lambda x:list(nltk.bigrams(x.split(' ')))).array
    #flatten list of array
    allTokens = [i for i in list(itertools.chain(*cleanTweetArray)) if i!='']

    num = 10
    dfCount = pd.Series(allTokens).value_counts()[:num].reset_index()
    dfCount.columns = ["Bigram", "Frequency"]
    dfCount['Bigram'] = dfCount['Bigram'].map(lambda x:' '.join(x))
    dfCount.sort_values("Frequency", inplace = True)
    dfCount.plot.barh(x='Bigram', y = 'Frequency', title = "Top 10 Bigram - %s"%yValue, ax=ax[no], legend=False)
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
